172
00:16:10,013 --> 00:16:10,971
...es urgente...

173
00:16:11,054 --> 00:16:12,723
...quiérame...

174
00:16:12,806 --> 00:16:14,224
...y por favor...

175
00:16:14,266 --> 00:16:16,310
