187
00:17:52,322 --> 00:17:54,116
Sí, yo salía con su hermana.

188
00:17:54,157 --> 00:17:56,784
- ¿Su hermana?
- Sí, Phyllis.

189
00:17:56,993 --> 00:17:58,912
